$interpreted: Crushfang: Damn miners hiding out here again!
Crushfang: Tsk! Just a Helmetal Thief...
Razorclaw: Haha, you're too impulsive. You ought to learn to calm down!
Crushfang: You've gotten soft since your son was born.
Crushfang: What happened to the fearsome "Bloody Claw"?
Crushfang: Did the humans replace him with a teddy bear? Hmm? I want my war buddy back!
Razorclaw: ...Well that was then, this is now. It's normal to soften up after becoming a father.
Crushfang: Your son... Dagger, is it?
Crushfang: Who knew he'd change you so much.
Razorclaw: He's going through that mischievous phase now, running around all the time. Seriously, Bilgebats are easier to catch...
Razorclaw: Hope he doesn't turn out like you when he grows up.
Crushfang: Nothing wrong with being like me! I can teach him—
Dumb Bear Soldier: Mayday! Mayday!

Dumb Bear Soldier: Illegal Miners at the west entrance! 
We can't hold out much longer!
Crushfang: Curse those bastards!
Razorclaw: Crushfang, let's go help!
Crushfang: Hurting my friend!? Oh, you're in for it now...!
Crushfang: Bastards! Don't run!
Razorclaw: Slow down, Crushfang. We should tend to the injured first!
Crushfang: I'll leave that to you. I'm going after those miners!
Razorclaw: It's too dangerous, you can't do it on your own...
Crushfang: Shut it!  Just sit here and wait!
Crushfang: Woah!
Razorclaw: Crushfang, you alright!?
Crushfang: Razorclaw!
Crushfang: Razorclaw! Razorclaw! Speak to me!
Razorclaw: ...It... it hurts... I think they hit an organ...
Crushfang: Hang in there, I'll get you back!
Crushfang: Damnit, why am I so weak...

Razorclaw: Won't... make it...*cough*...*cough*...
Please... take care of... Dagger...

Crushfang: Come on now! You can take care of your own son! 
Aren't we bringing him on patrol together!?
Crushfang: You still need to see his Rite of Passage!
Bear Scout: Chieftain, illegal miners in Totemtaff again! They're heading west!
Dagger: Damn humans! Time to teach them a lesson!
Crushfang: Dagger, wait here.
Dagger: Let me come with you! Humans are easy targets!
Crushfang: Hmph! This isn't child's play! You could get yourself killed!
Dagger: I'm no—
Crushfang: Enough. You're staying here.
